 ## 📡 API Reference
 
+### Connection / contacts
+
+| Method | Path | Purpose |
+|--------|------|---------|
+| GET  | `/api/auth/qr`            | Current QR (also via `/ws/qr`) |
+| GET  | `/api/auth/status`        | Connection status |
+| POST | `/api/auth/logout`        | Clear session |
+| GET  | `/api/contacts`           | List recent contacts |
